description:
Piece of Cake (1988)
Masterpiece Theater mini-series
Stars: Neil Dudgeon, George Anton, Boyd Gaines
IMDb: tt0157239
Website: http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/masterpiece/archive/116/116e.html

Piece of Cake follows the adventures, heartaches and rites of passage of the fighter pilots of RAF Hornet Squadron during World War II. It marks the coming of age of young men prepared to die for their country, whatever their own personal qualities. There are heroes in abundance and a rich cross-section of characters from the pilots to the back-up team at base. The other heroes are the planes themselves. Under ex-Red Arrows aerobatics team leader Ray Hanna (Flyboys), this series features some of the most exciting aerial photography and special effects ever seen.

Encoding comments: Sharpened and adjusted contrast and gamma to improve video quality. (Source DVD quality is mediocre, equivalent to VHS.)
